race.description: Pro Lift Garage Doors Mdn Plate
race.comment: PARAMOUNT PLUS (3) had placed in both runs back from a spell, holding his ground in a handy maiden at Sandown Hillside last time out. Drawn well for this and a repeat of last time goes close. GOOD HARMONY (11) ran a credible race on debut at Bairnsdale when well supported and should be further improved for it. No shock to see her improve. AITU (7) did enough fresh at Bendigo when sneaking into third in a strongly run maiden. Fitter for that and can give cheek. SUPREME SAILING (12) can run well on debut. DELA BELLA (5) solid effort last start when resuming, beaten 1.5 lengths into fifth over 1300m at Bendigo. Fitter and not out of this.
